RBG Smart System: Procurement & Quoting Intelligence
Overview

The RBG Smart System is a full-stack automated procurement and dynamic quoting platform developed for a specialized graphic design and signage company. It addresses critical operational bottlenecks by transforming manual supplier price tracking into a data-driven, automated workflow. 
The Problem

The client faced significant manual admin overhead in two key areas:

    Procurement Inefficiency: Manually checking prices across multiple regional suppliers (Maizey, Stixo, Falcon) was time-consuming and often led to missed savings. 

    Quoting Bottlenecks: Calculating job costs (materials + labor + overhead) manually delayed customer responses and created room for human error. 

The Solution

An end-to-end IT system that integrates real-time market data with business logic to optimize profit margins. 
Key Features

    Market Intelligence Engine: Automatically compares material prices across diverse suppliers to identify the lowest market rates. 

    Dynamic Job Quoter: A professional calculator that factors in real-time material costs, labor hours, and job complexity to generate instant, accurate quotes. 

    Inventory & Stock Tracking: Real-time monitoring of workshop stock levels with an integrated manual update interface. 

    Order Automator: Generates automated order request drafts to suppliers via a "Lead-to-Cash" pipeline, streamlining the purchasing process. 

    Cloud Integration: Built on a NoSQL backbone for persistent, secure, and remote data access. 

Tech Stack

    Language: Python (Pandas, NumPy) 

    Frontend: Streamlit 

    Database: Google Firebase (Firestore) 

    DevOps: Environment-specific configuration for local and cloud deployment. 

Project Architecture

    supplier_sync.py: A data ingestion script that cleans and pushes the latest supplier data to the cloud. 

    app.py: The main user interface providing the Dashboard, Quoter, and Ordering tools. 

    serviceAccountKey.json: Secure authentication for Firebase administrative access. 

Impact

    90% Reduction in manual quoting time. 

    100% Price Accuracy by eliminating manual spreadsheet entries. 

    Direct Revenue Growth enabled by faster customer response times and optimized material procurement. 

